videos.headline: Baker connects with Smith on 15-yard SDSU TD
videos.description: Carson Baker drops a pass right into the arms of Kobe Smith in the end zone to score a 15-yard touchdown and give San Diego State a 7-0 lead over Utah State in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baker connects with Smith on 15-yard SDSU TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shelley connects with Thompkins on long TD pass before halftime
videos.description: Jason Shelley throws the deep ball to Deven Thompkins, who makes the grab in the corner of the end zone to score a 37-yard touchdown as the first half comes to an end.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shelley connects with Thompkins on long TD pass before halftime) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bell makes diving effort for SDSU TD
videos.description: Greg Bell makes the catch then makes his way up the sideline and dives into the end zone to score a 29-yard SDSU touchdown to extend their lead to 31-7 over Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bell makes diving effort for SDSU TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Byrd breaks free for 73-yard SDSU TD
videos.description: Jordan Byrd takes the handoff and takes off down the field to score a 73-yard touchdown to extend the SDSU lead to 38-7 over Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Byrd breaks free for 73-yard SDSU TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET
